    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Paperclip 上傳驗證]]></title>
    <link href="http://hechien.github.com/octopress/blog/2012/03/23/paperclip-shang-chuan-yan-zheng/"/>
    <updated>2012-03-23T11:44:00+08:00</updated>
